================================================================================
                                   MOONLENS
                         Screen Translation Software
================================================================================

MoonLens is a lightweight screen translation tool for Windows that allows you
to capture any area of your screen and instantly translate the text within it.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                   FEATURES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  • Screen area selection with instant OCR text recognition
  • Real-time translation powered by Google Translate
  • Support for multiple languages:
      - Source languages: English, Spanish (more coming soon)
      - Target languages: English, Spanish, Japanese, Chinese, Korean
  • Customizable keyboard shortcuts for quick access
  • Dark and Light mode interface
  • Floating translation popup for background mode
  • Bilingual interface (English and Spanish)
  • Start with Windows option

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 REQUIREMENTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  • Windows 10/11
  • Internet connection for translation services
  • Windows OCR language packs for desired source languages

